rComments: I found her explanations of problems unclear and hard to follow. All she did was read off the lecture slides that were made for her by the flipitphysics company. She didn't seem to care that much about teaching. Office hours were not very helpful, I would not recommend her.
Lectures are fairly clear, only complaint is that she'll interrupt lecture to tell the one kid in the back of the lecture hall to get off his/her phone/laptop. Tests are similar to homework problems.
